sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 用户
    participant Brain
    participant Conductor
    participant Engine as Aeloop Loop
    participant Coder
    participant Tester
    participant Human as 人工 Gate
    participant Audit as Events / Audit
    User->>Brain: 自然语言需求 / PRD
    Brain->>Conductor: versioned TaskContract
    Conductor->>Conductor: schema、policy、workflow、budget 校验
    Conductor->>Engine: RunPlan
    Engine->>Coder: Prompt + Context
    Coder-->>Engine: structured candidate
    Engine->>Audit: run_started / node / usage
    Engine->>Human: G1：是否发送给 tester？
    Human-->>Engine: approve 或 reject
    Engine->>Tester: candidate + contract + evidence
    Tester-->>Engine: pass 或 findings
    alt tester reject
        Engine->>Human: G2：是否把 findings 返回 coder？
        Human-->>Engine: approve 或 escalate
        Engine->>Coder: fix-forward findings
    else tester pass
        Engine->>Human: G3：最终授权
        Human-->>Engine: approve 或 reject
    end
    Engine->>Audit: EvidenceBundle + checkpoint
    Engine-->>Conductor: run result
    Conductor-->>User: 状态、证据、待决策项
